1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,840
[EP. 02] Before the Awkwardness Fades

2
00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:12,940
Ha! It’s like I haven’t seen the sunlight for years.

3
00:00:12,940 --> 00:00:16,120
I almost lived in the studio during the break.

4
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:18,160
Oh right!
You’re preparing for the competition.

5
00:00:18,520 --> 00:00:19,840
What did you guys do during the break?

6
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:21,460
During b-break?

7
00:00:21,460 --> 00:00:23,120
I just stayed home.

8
00:00:24,220 --> 00:00:25,080
Hmm...

9
00:00:25,080 --> 00:00:27,920
You’re so mean!
How come you never called me?

10
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:31,400
Sorry, sorry! The class ended late.

11
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:34,040
Argh! The School of Arts is too far!

12
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:36,580
Wook! How have you been?

13
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:41,480
Oh, hey!
I just stayed home the whole time.

14
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:44,230
Wook…

15
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:46,760
You never called me during the break, either!

16
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:47,740
Oh…

17
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:49,740
I was a bit…busy.

18
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:53,980
Yeah right.

19
00:00:53,980 --> 00:00:55,120
You don’t have friends anyway.

20
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:56,620
That’s not true!!

21
00:01:03,540 --> 00:01:04,720
Hey!

22
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:10,920
She looks prettier
after not seeing her for a long time…

23
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:27,560
Sh-Should we all eat together?
It’s been awhile.?

24
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,100
Huh? Hello?

25
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:31,360
Oh, yes.

26
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:33,900
I’m on my way! Okay.

27
00:01:33,910 --> 00:01:35,700
I’ve got to go.

28
00:01:35,700 --> 00:01:38,180
Hey, but I just got here!

29
00:01:38,180 --> 00:01:39,840
You were late!

30
00:01:40,620 --> 00:01:41,920
I have to go!

31
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,840
Okay…

32
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,840
See you later!

33
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,900
Was it..

34
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,840
Gun Ha..?

35
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:55,680
Timing
a bus that rarely returns once you miss it.

36
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:21,320
A Day Before Us Season 2

